@startuml
title 11 - Fluxo Alternativo - Estoque Indisponível

autonumber
actor Buyer as Comprador
participant "Marketplace Web" as FE
participant "Marketplace BFF" as BFF
participant "Shipping Promise Service" as Promise
participant "Product Catalog Service" as Catalog
participant "Inventory Service" as Inventory
participant "Checkout Service" as Checkout
queue "Kafka" as Kafka

Comprador -> FE: Solicita frete para produto
FE -> BFF: GET /api/web/v1/products/{skuId}/page?zipCode={cep}
BFF -> Promise: POST /shipping-promises/
Promise -> Catalog: POST /products/physical-info/batch
Catalog --> Promise: Dados físicos do SKU
Promise -> Inventory: POST /inventory/availability/batch
Inventory --> Promise: availableQuantity=0
Promise --> BFF: available=false, unavailableReason="No inventory available"
BFF --> FE: Produto sem opção de entrega
FE --> Comprador: Exibe indisponibilidade de estoque

== Tentativa tardia durante confirmação ==
Comprador -> FE: Tenta confirmar checkout antigo
FE -> BFF: POST /api/web/v1/checkouts/{checkoutId}/confirm
BFF -> Checkout: POST /checkouts/{checkoutId}/confirm
Checkout -> Kafka: CheckoutConfirmedIntegrationEvent
Kafka -> Inventory: ReserveInventoryCommand
Inventory -> Inventory: Valida saldo insuficiente
Inventory -> Kafka: InventoryReservationFailedIntegrationEvent
Kafka -> Checkout: Evento de falha para auditoria/estado
Kafka -> BFF: Sem resposta síncrona direta

@enduml
